and I'm expecting a headache later.

270
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:09,320
- But Anna wants to come.
- What? No.

271
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:12,200
What about Matt?
You could see him, talk to him.

272
00:30:12,280 --> 00:30:14,680
