312
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:59,000
The fire wasn't an accident, was it?

313
00:33:59,080 --> 00:34:01,160
- What did you see?
- Matt?

314
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:02,680
Those berries aren't getting any fresher.

315
00:34:02,760 --> 00:34:04,880
